      ],
      "text": "请！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00068",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s03",
      "scene_no": 3,
      "seq_global": 68,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "众人同下。（四龙套、四下手、郭淮、王朗、曹真自下场门同上。四龙套、四上手、关兴、张苞、诸葛亮自上场门同上，同对阵。）",
      "text_length": 58
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00069",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 69,
      "seq_in_scene": 1,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "关兴听令！",
      "text_length": 5
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00070",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 70,
      "seq_in_scene": 2,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴"
      ],
      "text": "在！",
      "text_length": 2
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00071",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 71,
      "seq_in_scene": 3,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "命你去至阵前，就说汉丞相请司徒阵前答话。",
      "text_length": 20
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00072",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 72,
      "seq_in_scene": 4,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴"
      ],
      "text": "得令！曹营将士听着：汉丞相请司徒阵前答话。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00073",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 73,
      "seq_in_scene": 5,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王朗"
      ],
      "text": "老夫来也。来者敢是卧龙先生么？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00074",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 74,
      "seq_in_scene": 6,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "然也！阵前来的莫非是王司徒么？",
      "text_length": 15
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00075",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 75,
      "seq_in_scene": 7,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王朗"
      ],
      "text": "岂敢！久闻先生抱经世之才，隐居隆中，躬耕南阳，淡泊明志，自比管仲、乐毅。既然出山，就该扶保明主，为何辅助刘备，岂非背大道而逆人情哉！",
      "text_length": 66
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00076",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 76,
      "seq_in_scene": 8,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "想吾昭烈皇帝，乃大汉中山靖王之后，孝景皇帝阁下之玄孙。统领义师，扫荡海内，安汉兴刘，匡扶汉室，正合大道而顺人情，岂同那曹丕篡逆之贼也？",
      "text_length": 67
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00077",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 77,
      "seq_in_scene": 9,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "王朗"
      ],
      "text": "盖天数有变，神器更易，而归有德之人，此自然之理。汉室数尽，天下争锋——董卓叛逆；傕、氾行凶；袁术僭号于寿春；袁绍称雄于邺上；刘表占据荆州；吕布虎吞徐郡。社稷倾覆，生灵涂炭。我太祖武皇帝扫清四海，平定八荒，并非以权势所取，实天命所归也。世祖文帝，圣神文武以膺大统，法唐尧禅位虞舜之道以治天下，岂非天心人意？古人有云：顺天者昌，逆天者亡。先生幸勿逆天行事，枉费辛劳。倘若马前归顺吾主，定不失封侯之位！",
      "text_length": 198
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00078",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 78,
      "seq_in_scene": 10,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "expression",
      "mode_label": "笑",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "啊哈哈哈……",
      "text_length": 6
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00079",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 79,
      "seq_in_scene": 11,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "吾道你是汉朝大老元臣，必有高论，不料你竟是一派胡言，令人好笑也！",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00080",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 80,
      "seq_in_scene": 12,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮二六板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "王朗你本是汉老臣，食君之禄当报国恩。匡扶汉室你全不论，兴刘安汉心无毫分。助桀为虐篡了汉鼎，甘心愿为谄媚臣。竟敢在马前胡乱论，细听老夫说分明。",
      "text_length": 70
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00081",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 81,
      "seq_in_scene": 13,
      "page_no": 3,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "老夫今有一言，你且听着：昔日桓灵之世，汉统凌替，十常侍作乱于先，董卓、傕、氾相继而起，劫夺圣驾，残害生灵，国乱岁凶，苍生涂炭。以致狼心狗肺之徒，皆食禄于庙堂；奴颜婢膝之辈，均垂绅于殿阁。幸皇天不绝汉嗣，昭烈皇帝亲承汉统，践位西川。吾今奉幼主之命，兴师前来讨贼。你既为叛逆之https://scripts.xikao.com/play/030270052021-11-24臣，就该潜身缩首，怎么还敢在这行伍之前，讲什么天数？我把你这皓首的匹夫，苍髯的老贼，罪孽深重，恶贯满盈，神鬼之所共怒，天地之所不容。有道是：乱臣贼子，人人得而诛之。我恨不得食尔之肉也！",
      "text_length": 277
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00082",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 82,
      "seq_in_scene": 14,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "罪恶滔天人人恨，我骂死你这老谗臣。",
      "text_length": 17
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00083",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 83,
      "seq_in_scene": 15,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "王朗"
      ],
      "text": "一席话骂的我无言可论，气满胸膛我有话难云。",
      "text_length": 21
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00084",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 84,
      "seq_in_scene": 16,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "stage_direction",
      "mode_label": "stage_direction",
      "speakers": [],
      "text": "王朗落马，死。四龙套、四下手抬王朗同下。曹真、郭淮同下。",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00085",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 85,
      "seq_in_scene": 17,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "关兴"
      ],
      "text": "王朗落马已死，曹兵退去。",
      "text_length": 12
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00086",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 86,
      "seq_in_scene": 18,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "spoken",
      "mode_label": "白",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "曹真虽然兵退，岂能甘心？今晚定来偷营。众将暂且回营去者！",
      "text_length": 28
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00087",
      "play_id": "03027005",
      "scene_id": "03027005_s04",
      "scene_no": 4,
      "seq_global": 87,
      "seq_in_scene": 19,
      "page_no": 4,
      "type": "aria",
      "mode_label": "西皮摇板",
      "speakers": [
        "诸葛亮"
      ],
      "text": "老夫奉命出西秦，胸抱雄才敌万人。王朗阵前已丧命，安排人马破曹真。",
      "text_length": 32
    },
    {
      "event_id": "03027005_e00088",
